lls}}\n{{Wiktionary|Mindfulness}}\n{{Commons category}}\n{{refbegin}}\n;Origins\n* {{cite book |last=McMahan |first=David L. | name-list-format = vanc |year=2008 |title=The Making of Buddhist Modernism |place= |publisher= Oxford University Press |isbn= 978-0195183276}}\n* {{cite book |last=Braun |first =Erik Braun| name-list-format = vanc  | year =2016 | title =The Birth of Insight. Meditation, Modern Buddhism, and the Burmese Monk Ledi Sayadaw | publisher =The University Of Chicago Press}}\n* {{cite book |last=Wilson |first=Jeff | name-list-format = vanc |year=2014 |title= Mindful America: Meditation and the Mutual Transformation of Buddhism and American Culture |publisher= Oxford University Press}}\n\n;Buddhism\n* {{cite book |last=Nyanaponika |title=The Heart of Buddhist Meditation: Satipa\u1e6d\u1e6dh\u0101na : a Handbook of Mental Training Based on the Buddha's Way of Mindfulness, with an Anthology of Relevant Texts Translated from the Pali and Sanskrit}}\n* {{cite book | first = William | last = Hart | name-list-format = vanc | date = 2011 | title = The Art of Living: Vipassana Meditation As Taught by S.N. Goenka | publisher = Pariyatti }}\n;Psychology\n* {{Citation |last=Didonna |first=Fabrizio | name-list-format = vanc |year=2008 |title=Clinical Handbook of Mindfulness |publisher= Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=}} \n* {{cite book | first1 = Amanda | last1 = Ie | first2 = Christelle T. | last2 = Ngnoumen | first3 = Ellen J. | last3 = Langer | name-list-format = vanc | date = 2014 | title = The Wiley Blackwell Handbook of Mindfulness (Two Volumes) | publisher = John Wiley & Sons  }}\n;Popular\n* {{cite book | title = Wherever You Go, There You Are: Mindfulness Meditation in Everyday Life | publisher = Hyperion Books | date = 2005 | isbn = 1401307787 }}\n\n;Critical\n* {{cite journal |last1=Levman |first1=Bryan | name-list-format = vanc |title=Putting sm\u1e5bti back into sati (Putting remembrance back into mindfulness) |journal=Journal of the Oxford Ce